          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Use to design a Throw </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">motion-law, in which a </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">return</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> segment follows </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">immediately</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> after a </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">rise</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> segment.</text></para>
